5 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT ELIMINATING THE DONATION OF PADDLEFISH EGGS FOR
6 PROCESSING AND MARKETING AS CAVIAR; AMENDING SECTIONS 87-6-202, 87-6-206, AND 87-6-707,
7 MCA; REPEALING SECTION 87-4-601, MCA; AND PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE EFFECTIVE DATE.”
